meer nodig! Het geïntegreerde harnas biedt comfortabele en veilige controle tijdens het lopen. Jouw hond zit veilig en comfortabel in de jas. Praktisch en stijlvol voor de winter!<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["template--20109320978756__1257f402-04b3-4e08-93b3-6d6dd0b5f272-text-1"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"display_id":false,"visibility":"always-display","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/gif_4_0d76c123-6c4d-4065-9a4d-51e310d5797c.webp","video_autoplay":true,"video_loop":true,"height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","full_desktop_width":false,"content_layout":"no-overlap","desktop_media_width":50,"layout":"text_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_full_media_width":false,"mobile_direction":"normal","mobile_image_quanlity":"2","mobile_content_alignment":"left","mobile_padding_top":0,"mobile_padding_bottom":16,"desktop_padding_top":36,"desktop_padding_bottom":36,"custom_colors_background":"#2e2a39","custom_gradient_background":"","custom_colors_text":"#ffffff","custom_colors_solid_button_background":"#dd1d1d","custom_colors_solid_button_text":"#ffffff","custom_colors_outline_button":"#dd1d1d","custom_section_colors_background":"#ffffff","custom_section_gradient_background":""}},"debb262c-7966-437e-9293-3d712dea0416":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"template--20109320978756__debb262c-7966-437e-9293-3d712dea0416-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h4>Gezellige hondenjas met een zachte fleecevoering<\/h4><p>Met onze knusse hondenjas, die een <strong>zachte fleecevoering<\/strong> heeft, kan jouw harige vriend het hele jaar door de natuur verkennen. De jas is speciaal ontworpen om jouw hond te beschermen tegen koude wind en lage temperaturen.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["template--20109320978756__debb262c-7966-437e-9293-3d712dea0416-text-1"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"display_id":false,"visibility":"always-display","image":"shopify:\/\/sh